description.en: Blastoise Inu is  a fan token made by our core team of 22 members around the world. Made up of a solidity dev, expert graphic designer, game developer and of course some seasoned crypto veterans with extensive experience in marketing and connections in crypto world. The token plans to set a new standard in Ethereum chain for tokens. Blastoise Inu is already in development stages for an upcoming DEX, NFT collection , and a massive partnership with a well known token.
